  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punch, Grab, and Throw your friendships away in Mini Bash! Join your friends online or locally in this chaotic party brawler and compete in a variety of physics-based mini-games! Laugh, cry, and never speak to your friends again!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY YOUR WAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play locally with up to 4 or online with up to 8 of your friends, but whatever you choose, make sure to make some enemies along the way!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>EXPLODE YOUR FRIENDS!</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DESTROY YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Punch, grab, toss, dance, explode, climb, laugh, and cry your way to the top of the scoreboard!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>GO CRAZY GO STUPID!</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMPETE FOR GEMS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compete in the board game mode to see who truly is the worst person in your friend group!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>SO SHINY!</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/53fbe8a6cae11f096dbc1100f1ac7cf9.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/53fbe8a6cae11f096dbc1100f1ac7cf9.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/53fbe8a6cae11f096dbc1100f1ac7cf9.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CLAIM YOUR THRONE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Revel in the defeat of your so called friends!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>YOUR THE BEST AROUND!</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/3584d76cb8c0e97037578a80fa375e13.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/3584d76cb8c0e97037578a80fa375e13.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/3584d76cb8c0e97037578a80fa375e13.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></h2></h2></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punch, Grab, and Throw your friendships away in Mini Bash! Join your friends online or locally in this chaotic party brawler and compete in a variety of physics-based mini-games! Laugh, cry, and never speak to your friends again!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY YOUR WAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play locally with up to 4 or online with up to 8 of your friends, but whatever you choose, make sure to make some enemies along the way!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>EXPLODE YOUR FRIENDS!</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DESTROY YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Punch, grab, toss, dance, explode, climb, laugh, and cry your way to the top of the scoreboard!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>GO CRAZY GO STUPID!</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3e